      "acceptanceCriteria": "Goal (c): commercial FEA solvers (Ansys 2019R1, Abaqus 6.14) widely used in medical device industry with active SQA documentation; anomaly lists reviewed by each lab. [Nagaraja Table 1, SQA]",
      "rationale": "Three labs (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) used commercial solvers with documented SQA processes. No major anomalies relevant to compression-bending simulation reported in vendor anomaly lists.",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018"
    },
    {
