      "acceptanceCriteria": "Goal (b): grid convergence observed via three mesh refinement levels per lab; QoI variation <2% between fine and finest meshes. Formal Richardson extrapolation not performed. [Nagaraja §2.3, Table 1]",
      "rationale": "Each lab independently ran mesh-convergence sweeps. Construct stiffness and yield force converged to within 2% across the two finest mesh densities. Richardson extrapolation deferred per V&V 40 (b) gradation.",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018"
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
