    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Model accuracy met pre-established criterion of <10% difference between FEA and experiment for all three QoIs (stiffness 1.5% E/D, yield load 1.1% E/D, force at 40 mm 1.3% E/D). Critical stress location (rod midshaft) matched experimental failure mode. Test-conditions factor shortfall (achievedLevel 1 vs requiredLevel 3) is acknowledged and offset by N=11 sample size which exceeds typical spinal-device testing recommendations.",
